### 
### Scenario: Need to change user password or root password on multiple servers.  
###
### Solution:  Automate this process using ansible playbook.  
#
#  
#
### Inventory file 
#
## cat /etc/ansible/hosts 

[devservers] 

devserver1 

devserver2 

devserver3 

devserver4 

  

[testservers] 

testserver1 

testserver2 

  

[webservers] 

webnode1 

webnode2 

  
